to give write permission:on Desktop(if the directory is in desktop)sudo chown -R dipto project_name
to create nodejs project:sudo npx express-generator mock
node app.js                    

npm install mysql
to hide info:create .env in node_modules
create .gitignore on node_modules ->.env 
node_modules
 sudo npm install dotenv
to avoid re run:sudo npm install --save-dev nodemon
on package.json:scripts->"start": "nodemon app.js"
now npm start
to saltsync and hashsync password:sudo npm install
 bcrypt

sudo npm i jsonwebtoken
sudo npm install --save cors //to allow the client to access the server
